OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FBy Lily Ford, ITV News Multimedia
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FA new report is set to recommend a
OL,10,Ffour-week summer holiday across
OL,11,FEngland for the benefit of teachers,
OL,12,Fpupils, and parents.
OL,14,FThe proposal, funded by the Nuffield
OL,15,FFoundation and authored by three , is
OL,16,Fpart of a wider suggestion to
OL,17,Fcompletely reform the school calendar.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/19
