OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FThe is set to be published after
OL,7,FEaster, centred around the gaps in
OL,8,Flearning that are going to emerge for
OL,9,Fthe Covid-19 generation.
OL,11,FIts lead author, Professor Lee Elliot
OL,12,FMajor of the University of Exeter,
OL,13,Fspoke to ITV News about the key pieces
OL,14,Fof advice his report is recommending
OL,15,Fschools and the government take
OL,16,Fforward - including moving a week from
OL,17,Fthe summer break to the autumn.
OL,19,FBut would it work? And what would be
OL,20,Fthe downsides?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
