OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FAs well as this, staff training days
OL,7,Fcould be compacted into one week
OL,8,Finstead of spread across the year.
OL,10,F"What we're doing is looking at the
OL,11,Fprospects of the Covid generation -
OL,12,Fwhat can happen to all these young
OL,13,Fchildren who were affected by Covid,"
OL,14,FProfessor Major, who produced the
OL,15,Freport alongside Professor Stephen
OL,16,FMachin and Mr Andrew Eyles from the
OL,17,FLondon School of Economics, explained
OL,18,Fto ITV News.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/19
