OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,F"Essentially, we're saying there's
OL,7,Fgonna be a challenge over the next
OL,8,Fdecade for these kids.
OL,10,F"So what we were trying to do, given
OL,11,Fthat the government was saying to us,
OL,12,F'Look, we don't have any money. So if
OL,13,Fyou've got any ideas, things that
OL,14,Fdon't cost that much...'
OL,16,F"When we looked at the evidence, we
OL,17,Ffelt that there was some good
OL,18,Fcompelling arguments."
OL,20,FHow would it benefit teachers,
OL,21,Fparents, and children, respectively?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/19
