OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FA lot of the conclusions are also
OL,7,Fbased around prioritising the
OL,8,Fwellbeing of the country's teachers.
OL,10,FProfessor Major said that they found
OL,11,Fthe autumn term proved "really
OL,12,Ffatiguing" for staff and pupils, and
OL,13,Fadding an extra week would help "for
OL,14,Feducational reasons".
OL,16,FAnother option is to have another week
OL,17,Fadded to the half-term in February.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/19
