OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FFinally, Professor Major said that
OL,7,Fsteep childcare costs and holiday
OL,8,Fcosts has made the six weeks "a real
OL,9,Fchallenge" for many parents.
OL,11,FBut a shorter school holiday could
OL,12,Fprove to be a resolution to soaring
OL,13,Fprices.
OL,15,F"We just believe that if you evened
OL,16,Fout some of those breaks across the
OL,17,Fyear, it's just a bit more manageable
OL,18,Ffor those parents," he said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/19
