OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,F"Maybe we could have different regions
OL,7,Fstaggering this summer break so that
OL,8,Fholiday costs might come down. We have
OL,9,Fthese horrendously big hikes in
OL,10,Fholidays during that six weeks.
OL,12,F"I think those that are resistant to
OL,13,Fit are often the very few people that
OL,14,Fare rich enough to be able to afford a
OL,15,Fsix week holiday - that's not many
OL,16,Fpeople."
OL,18,FWhat do teachers and parents think?
