OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FA recent poll by the Teacher Tapp app
OL,7,Ffound teachers were divided over
OL,8,Fwhether the summer holidays should be
OL,9,Fshortened and by how much.
OL,11,FWhile 33% backed keeping the summer
OL,12,Fbreak at six weeks, 35% wanted it
OL,13,Fshortened to five weeks and 29%
OL,14,Fpreferred cutting it to four.
OL,16,FA statement from teachers' union
OL,17,FNASUWT said the proposal to shorten
OL,18,Fsummer holidays are "nothing new" and
OL,19,Fthat the education system requires
OL,20,F"substantially more investment in
OL,21,Fservices for children and families".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/19
