OL,6,F"Depressingly, what is also not new is
OL,7,Fthe lack of credible evidence
OL,8,Fdemonstrating that such changes would
OL,9,Fimprove educational standards."
OL,11,FThe new research for this project
OL,12,Ffocused on the gaps in learning that
OL,13,Fwill emerge for the Covid generation,
OL,14,Fbut the wider recommendations for the
OL,15,Fschool calendar is based on a review
OL,16,Fof existing evidence.
