OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FParentkind, a national charity that
OL,7,Faims to bridge the gap between parents
OL,8,Fand schools, supported Professor
OL,9,FMajor's claim that those who struggle
OL,10,Fover the six-week break are much more
OL,11,Fin favour of its reduction.
OL,13,FFrank Young, director of research and
OL,14,Fpolicy at Parentkind said: "For
OL,15,Fparents, six weeks is a long time and
OL,16,Fmanaging annual leave and childcare to
OL,17,Fcover the summer holidays will be a
OL,18,Fchallenge most parents will be
OL,19,Ffamiliar with. Many will face the six-
OL,20,Fweek summer break with dread.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/19
