OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,F"When we spoke to almost 7,000 parents
OL,7,Fin Wales about Welsh government
OL,8,Fproposals to reduce the six week
OL,9,Fsummer holiday parents were split in
OL,10,Fresponse, with a small majority of
OL,11,Fparents in support.
OL,13,F"Families who really struggle over the
OL,14,Fsix week summer break were much more
OL,15,Fenthusiastic about the proposals for a
OL,16,Fmore even school year and shorter
OL,17,Fsummer holiday.
