OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FMr Young added that a solution must be
OL,7,Ffound that works for teachers,
OL,8,Fparents, and children, and that
OL,9,Fparents should be consulted on any
OL,10,Fchanges to the school calendar.
OL,12,FWhat are some of the major criticisms?
OL,14,FProfessor Major acknowledges that it's
OL,15,Fcutting into holiday time, but
OL,16,Freiterated the proposal is about
OL,17,Frebalancing the holiday rather than
OL,18,Freducing it.
