OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FHe said many people believe that the
OL,7,Feducation system should function as it
OL,8,Falways has, with some teachers being
OL,9,F"stuck in their ways."
OL,11,F"I just think on balance, think about
OL,12,Fthat long-term in the winter.
OL,14,F"When everyone's struggling,
OL,15,Feveryone's got colds and it's really
OL,16,Fhard... I just think that extra week
OL,17,Fin October would be much more
OL,18,Fbeneficial."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G16/19
