OL,3,CWould a four-week summer school
OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FHe added that it is more likely to be
OL,7,Fbetter weather in the weeks during the
OL,8,Fsummer, but drawing comparisons to
OL,9,Fother countries who have longer or
OL,10,Fshorter holidays is not a powerful
OL,11,Fargument as they have completely
OL,12,Fdifferent education systems.
OL,14,FWhen could this come into affect?
OL,16,FProfessor Major explained that the
OL,17,Freport will be shared with schools and
OL,18,Fgovernments, but also with trusts that
OL,19,Fhave discretion over their summer
OL,20,Fholidays.
