OL,4,Choliday work?
OL,6,FUltimately, for many schools, it's up
OL,7,Fto them whether they change their
OL,8,Fcalendar.
OL,10,F"I think you'd have to sort of
OL,11,Fcoordinate it, so you don't have
OL,12,Fmayhem out there (if the) school down
OL,13,Fthe road (or) another school does a
OL,14,Fslightly different approach,"
OL,15,FProfessor Major added. You've got to
OL,16,Fbe careful with this.
OL,18,F"I suppose you'd want the government
OL,19,Fto support it, but a lot of it is down
OL,20,Fto schools, increasingly, on these
OL,21,Fissues."
